## DEV_MAN rules

- Work on **one project at a time** (this repo only) and follow `DEV_MAN/Plans/*` when referenced.
- Do not remove or break existing features unless explicitly asked.
- When adding features, prefer adding new modules and keeping old entrypoints working.
- Keep outputs stable: do not change file naming/paths without updating docs and reports.

